description:
FluxPup-1.10 Alpha

by oldyella

Released 17 Mar 2014

more info http://www.murga-linux.com/puppy/viewtopic.php?t=92653


Hello Everyone, 

 I have just got FluxPup-1.10 to an Alpha wanted to build new kernel but the kernel would not compile for me, so will be using 3.9.11 pae. This has fluxbox 1.3.5. Built using ubuntu precise 

 Get it here http://www.smokey01.com/Oldyeller/FluxPup/ It is 152mb 

 I removed jwm but will be making pets and uploading them to server just in case someone would want jwm.(don't know why   ). 

 Will be building some new programs just for FluxPup. There is no desk icons. 

 What has been Added: 

 pwidgets starts right up 
 wbar has all the desk icons plus a few more 
 opera has been put in and seamonkey is out 

 Enjoy testing 

 Cheers
